<C>__{carol}
<D>__{i laugh when i feel happy. sometimes just thinking of you made me laugh. i had a lot of that. and other times that wasn't enough. i had a lot of that too. i know you find it hard to believe, i'm happy just loving you.}
<C>__{doc}
<D>__{that doesn't hurt.}
